      "updated": 1773929023434,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Benefit Vocabulary\n- Availability != uptime\n- Reliability = recover + continue\n- Scalability = handle growth\n- Elasticity = auto grow/shrink\n- Predictability = expected cost/performance",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 163,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Benefit Vocabulary\n- Availability != uptime\n- Reliability = recover + continue\n- Scalability = handle growth\n- Elasticity = auto grow/shrink\n- Predictability = expected cost/performance",
